Assignment: 21
Find out the 3rd max value without sorting a list?
Ans:
l=[2,3,4,1,-10,-20]
for i in range(2):
    m=max(l)
    l.remove(m)
print max(l)

Assignment: 22
Convert list of tuples to tuple of list
Ans:
l=[(1,2),(2,3),(4,5)]
l1=[]
for i in l:
    l1.append(list(i))
print tuple(l1)
